"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"A close scrutiny of recent advertisements suggests that the soft-sell technique is now popular. By soft-sell technique we mean the one that favors a more emotive and less directive approach to promote a product, mainly focusing on the building of brand image. As a result, emotive words, most of which are pleasant adjectives, are greatly encouraged to use.\",\"timestamp\":1638955970,\"title\":\"Use of emotive words\"},\"digest\":\"Fji0mNBQTu3oX9AAI8JMiKRT26-SiCSRF-I8HTm4X_Q\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x336b83B9F8dA5A4aA8a0115b13D7dEbB5790C425\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"f8xRyiP77UgONAYjo3gS6bEKLnOpPLaS43RQoRVDSug\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"URLHaGeqtzqTB-djCcjHtOjz7N0s6yarpH2ojtq1AtM\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"yiVB0pQmwWJu7nVoMAr84FnB7f4S-PcHKpZfkdb66GWQDJTvuq_M4pJZEAO6XjW38K4urCiZ_u4L-_jr0GsmVg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x59923914366b3d3979dc3051044f054034f8c932eacae40dd996d57d7355aa987e856ecc85d1db62ee52a700614cb04df5800f3889734bcaeb5a1c7397d51a1b1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"f8xRyiP77UgONAYjo3gS6bEKLnOpPLaS43RQoRVDSug\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"URLHaGeqtzqTB-djCcjHtOjz7N0s6yarpH2ojtq1AtM\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"Fji0mNBQTu3oX9AAI8JMiKRT26-SiCSRF-I8HTm4X_Q\"}"